Ya the melles get more easier to get better equipment.  Well the melles also have more stats they need to increase to be more effective.  They need to look into strenght, dex, agility, stamina, hit point itmes, Armor Class, haste itmes, and resists.  I may have forgoten something or added something that most melles don't look for.  <br>
